entries.title: Optimism on Chinese stocks soars to five-year highs
entries.description: Money is flowing into mainland Chinese and Hong Kong stocks in ways not seen since 2018, according to research firm EPFR Global.

entries.title: Elon Musk says Twitter is ‘trending to breakeven’ after near bankruptcy
entries.description: Elon Musk tweeted Sunday that the last few months have been "extremely tough," but said that Twitter is "now trending to break even."

entries.title: The 7 most in-demand tech skills for freelancers—many pay more than $125 an hour
entries.description: Tech skills are in high demand, and many can pay more than $100 per hour. These include full stack developer, mobile app developer and web designer.

entries.title: U.S. military shoots down suspected Chinese surveillance balloon
entries.description: The U.S. military on Saturday shot down a suspected Chinese surveillance balloon, according to media reports.
